    <help>
	<![CDATA[
	
	Support Fixed payment<br>
	Salt key is a unique number which is use to identify the hash. It can be generated by either <br>
	1. Contacting client support and receive the salt value, OR <br>
	2. Create your own salt value and provide it to client support.<br><br>
	
	<div class="rb-help-payinvoice rb-processor-help">
			<b>NOTE</b>:-1. Please set webhook url on ccbill's end to:- <a href =#>www.your_website.com/index.php?option=com_payinvoice&amp;view=invoice&amp;task=notify&amp;</a><br>
		     2. Set approval url to <a href =#>www.your_website.com/index.php?option=com_payinvoice&amp;view=invoice&amp;task=complete&amp;invoice_number=%%invoice_number%%</a><br>
	
	</div>
	
	 <div class="hide rb-help-paycart rb-processor-help">
			<b>NOTE</b>:-1. Please set webhook url on ccbill's end to:- <a href =#>www.your_website.com/index.php?option=com_paycart&amp;view=invoice&amp;task=notify&amp;</a><br>
		     2. Set approval url to <a href =#>www.your_website.com/index.php?option=com_paycart&amp;view=invoice&amp;task=complete&amp;invoice_number=%%invoice_number%%</a><br>
	
	</div>
	
     ]]>	
	</help>

